			<h1>SAVE</h1>
			<h3>An Internet of Things enabled payment & tracking service that centralises all your payments and improves your payment experience making it seamless. It also helps you to manage and analyse your expenses efficiently & effectively.</h3>
		</header>
		<section>
			<span class="project-step-number">01</span>
			<h2>CHALLENGE</h2>
			<p>The aim of the project was to design a new generation of payment experiences across digital & physical touchpoints. Designing a service for the cashless society comes with its fair share of challenges. Security issues, data sharing between different stakeholders, privacy of personal data especially in a crowded environment while making payment and gaining of peopleâ€™s trust in using the different elements that makes up the cashless experience.<br/><br/>

			Currently people have too many cards to manage during payments, and also it can be time-consuming and difficult to manage and categorise the different types of expenses in their daily lives.</p>

