			<span class="project-step-number">02</span>
			<h2>PROCESS</h2>
			<p>Desk research was carried out in order to understand the currently state of the cashless society and how transactions are made. And which government policies and technological innovations are enabling the growth of the cashless society. 
			<br/><br/>
			User behaviour observation was carried out to get a deep understanding and empathise with the consumer's actions,their state of mind and their contextual environment when they make payments and manage their expenses. This research was analysed to build a particular persona and his user journey/experience was mapped out in order to identify the various pain points and opportunity areas. Multiple ideas were consolidated and a concept was finalised which was visualised through a storyboard.</p> 
			
